snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Release Trailer 2 (Telugu) | Prabhas, Rana | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli

Sikkama sikkeduthaa

Ringa ringa

Kaandhazhi kannuladhan 
Thalladi undhuputtan
Soodana soora bodha

Yethi vecha kungumamaa 
Paathane kannala 
Ketene unna pola 

Aaki vechu kenjanuma 
Thooki vechu konjanuma 
Manama kekuriye
Pechu nallalla

Ayy yedakuda iduppula 
Yekachakka madippula 
Uchakattathuku pona 
Air-u la

Adi medu pallam paathu na 
Sokki pona gar uh la 
Thooki vechu thakka poren
Ner-u la

Malyutham nadakkudha

snippet.description:
Una saga divina que comenz√≥ en la India‚Ä¶ ahora conquista el mundo.

#KantaraChapter1 Spanish (Espa√±ola) Trailer out now.

#Kantara

From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations.

snippet.description:
India vs Australia, 1st T20 Match Live Cricket Score | IND VS AUS Live Match Today, India Batting, 1st Innings

For Contact umerhafeez2022@gmail.com 

Topics to be covered in the live stream üëáüèªüëáüèª

India vs Australia Live Match Today 
India vs Australia Live Cricket Score 
IND vs AUS Live Match Today 
Cricket Live Score 
Live Cricket Match Today

When: Australia v India, 1st T20I, October 29, 2025, 19:15 hrs Local Time, 19:15 hrs AEDT, 13:45 hrs IST

Where: Manuka Oval, Canberra

What to expect: The nation's capital doesn't see a lot of men's international cricket at this time of the year so there still seems to be a tinge of newness to proceedings here. There's been unseasonal rain in most parts of Australia, but it's expected to clear by the time the opening T20I kicks off in Canberra. India vs Australia T20 Series 2025, IND vs AUS 1st Match Live Cricket Score, India vs Australia Live Cricket Match Commentary is being presented by UH Sports.

Team News

Australia

The Australian selectors have been busy shuffling the pack over the last week or so with their squads to give their certain and potential Test players enough preparation time for the Ashes while maintaining a strong enough group to combat India's challenge. A couple of unforeseen injuries have further complicated affairs, and that should open the doors for Josh Philippe to probably get a game as a specialist batter as Josh Inglis returns to the team. That does give the Aussies a very ominous looking batting line-up up and down the order, with special focus on Josh Hazlewood as he continues to wheel away at the top of his game. India vs Australia T20 Live Match will start at 1:45 IST, IND Vs AUS T20 Live Cricket Match Today, Will be played at Canberra, Oval, Australia..

Probable XI: Travis Head, Mitch Marsh (c), Josh Inglis (wk), Marcus Stoinis, Tim David, Mitch Owen, Josh Philippe, Nathan Ellis, Xavier Bartlett/Sean Abbott, Matthew Kuhnemann, Josh Hazlewood

India

Australia is in for a treat with many of the names on display in the Indian T20I setup, and the question really will be how they slot in Kuldeep Yadav ahead of one of their two all-rounders, Nitish Kumar Reddy and Washington Sundar.

Probable XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Tilak Varma, Suryakumar Yadav (c), Sanju Samson (wk), Shivam Dube, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar/Kuldeep Yadav, Varun Chakravarthy, Jasprit Bumrah, Arshdeep Singh

snippet.title: YAARA ME (Official Video) Harry Lather | Komal Chaudhary | Ishita Malik | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Hit Music presents this song ' Jan Base Meri Yaara Me' Sung by Harry Lather &  Komal Chaudhary. Lyrics by Bhadak Singh. Video Directed by MP Sega. Video by Sega Production

Click to create Instagram Reels on this Song:   

Song Credits:
Title : Yaara Me
Singer : Harry Lather &  Komal Chaudhary
Female Lead : Ishita Malik
Lyrics : Bhadak Singh
Music : Pinna Music
Director : MP Sega
Video : Sega Production
DOP : Jass Sudhan
Edit & Di : Gurjaan Rukh
Publicity Designs : Sega Designs
Production Team : Aman Gill, Sandeep Patter & Chirag Goyal
AD : Yogi Patter
Costume : Rajat Manchanda
Casting : Rekha Thakur
Project : Sumit Kajla 

Reel Promotion : Reel Nation
Spotify : Nyx Media


Lyrics:

Me Bichli Bichli Haandu Su re
Kuch bi smjh na aara
Do case holiye bari tere
Or pending pade 18

Tere mathe pe se latt madam
Mhari sheli pe se cut madam
Le ram nam tu ratt madam
Or shopping kr tu bazara me
Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me

Ree Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me

.....................
Tu Karta ni kam re kit te pisse aave se
Teri har gaadi ke chore kale shishe pave se

In baata ne de chod bawli 
kit te kitne karod bawli
ghata ghunaa or jod bawli
chode umar 18 me

Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me

ree Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki ghadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me
...........

ohho chakrr maree delhi chandigarh ke kam chal rhya se
harry lather ncr me tera naam chal rhya se

mhare charche se ghar ghar madam 
rapiye bhula dhar dhar madam 
ratee mahadev har har madam
re dilchaspi naa nara me

Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me

ree Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me


Kyu aave bhadke naam tera bade akhbara me
tu sabste ghna se albadi tu tere sare yaara me

teri chale ja cham cham chori
mhare black dog or rum chori
na kise baat ka gham chori
ham lere jissa YAARA me

Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me

snippet.title: Creedence Clearwater Revival - Have You Ever Seen The Rain (Fan Celebration Version)
snippet.description:
We are celebrating your comments for the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video. Thank you for supporting CCR! 

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.
